TopicTitle: Contract: rescue from biplane cockpit, shipwrecked over Kerbin

Articles.Content:
Firespitter rocks! As I'm closing on it I'm thinking "Why is that green?" Dude seems pretty happy about wrecking his biplane.

Funny thing was when he EVAd he not only instantly put on a space suit but he also applied mascara and became a girl.

Weird!
That's hilarious! I guess the game uses any part that holds kerbals for those rescue contracts.
Uuuuh... I dunno how I got here....
